{"tid":885282,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"恒大未來有計劃開設法律學院","createTime":"2018-11-01T08:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T00:31:47.000Z","uid":3017,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a5ac9b2424b627d89fe9bfd220f5cc3039367263","tid":885282,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:18:57.000Z","msg":"除了現有學科外，何順文透露恒大未來有計劃開設法律學院，但有別於現時港大、城大及中大課程，「其實全世界有好多研究，本科生唔適合讀法律，一個人的心志，廣闊的知識基礎唔夠。」他指希望將來開辦的法律學院，主要以研究生作起步，「我們會集中將來（畢業後）唔係做律師，可能是（研究）國際法、比較法。」他認為讀法律的出路不一定是做律師。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第時法律界都會有我地恆大既學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4770a86e0eb10140dd2eac895e22203be4aca562","tid":885282,"uid":15193,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:22:50.000Z","msg":"咪害人啦.."},{"pid":"a0491571730a0103fd10d89ff2542d61fdacc607","tid":885282,"uid":192808,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:26:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"436feb262820f93cc796d019dbe4ba9d041b51d5","tid":885282,"uid":162316,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:28:28.000Z","msg":"預計五年內恆大將打入三大<br />\n與港大城大並列為香港三大最佳學府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c866529310c7f28d539cbff79b58ee28b821579","tid":885282,"uid":198998,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:37:27.000Z","msg":"含大世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a6f2ba901ce05d01bb57a6fb77f988edc3330b","tid":885282,"uid":197563,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>恒大BLaw<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets